# SEO Rules

## SEO Goal

Build a modern construction system website with strong semantic relevance around:

* Metal Siding Panels
* Exterior Systems
* Fast-install Systems
* Modular Construction
* Buildability
* Construction Efficiency

The website should rank as a modern construction system brand,
NOT as a low-quality commodity supplier.

---

# Website SEO Structure

The website structure should follow:

Home
↙ Systems
↙ Applications
↙ Projects
↙ Contact

The website should maintain clear semantic hierarchy.

Avoid excessive page nesting.

---

# Homepage SEO Rules

Homepage should target:

Primary Keywords:

* metal siding panels
* exterior systems
* fast-install exterior systems

Secondary Keywords:

* modular construction systems
* prefab exterior systems
* construction efficiency

Homepage should communicate:

* modern construction
* installation simplicity
* exterior efficiency
* modular compatibility

Homepage should NOT become:

* a keyword stuffing page
* a factory introduction page
* a product dump page

---

# Systems Page SEO Rules

Systems pages should focus on:

* product systems
* installation simplicity
* exterior applications
* structure systems

Each systems page should include:

* product visuals
* applications
* installation system
* structure diagrams
* project references

---

# Product Category SEO Rules

Current categories include:

* Wood Grain Metal Siding Panels
* Stone Look Metal Siding Panels
* Brick Style Metal Siding Panels
* Fluted Metal Siding Panels
* Corrugated Metal Siding Panels

Each category page should contain:

* category introduction
* application scenarios
* installation advantages
* exterior visuals
* product structure
* project usage

Avoid thin category pages.

---

# Applications SEO Rules

Applications pages should target scenario-based searches.

Examples:

* prefab house exterior panels
* modular home siding
* container house wall systems
* warehouse exterior cladding

Applications pages should focus on:

* project suitability
* installation efficiency
* climate compatibility
* modern appearance

Applications pages should contain:

* real application visuals
* recommended systems
* installation advantages
* project examples

---

# Projects SEO Rules

Projects pages should build trust and semantic relevance.

Each project page should include:

* project type
* location or region
* exterior system used
* installation visuals
* before / after visuals
* application explanation

Projects should help support:

* trust
* installation credibility
* exterior system understanding

---

# Heading Structure Rules

Each page should contain:

* One H1 only
* Clear H2 hierarchy
* Semantic H3 structure

Avoid heading spam.

Headings should naturally include keywords.

---

# URL Rules

Use clean SEO-friendly URLs.

Examples:

/systems/metal-siding-panels
/systems/wood-grain-metal-siding-panels
/applications/prefab-houses
/projects/modular-home-project

Avoid:

* random numbers
* unreadable slugs
* long unnecessary URLs

---

# Image SEO Rules

All images should include descriptive ALT text.

Good examples:

* modern prefab house with wood grain metal siding
* fast-install exterior wall system installation
* stone look metal siding exterior project

Avoid:

* image1
* banner-final
* photo123

Images should support semantic SEO relevance.

---

# Internal Linking Rules

Pages should naturally connect:

Systems
↙ Applications
↙ Projects
↙ Contact

Applications should link to:

* relevant systems
* related projects

Projects should link to:

* systems used
* application scenarios

---

# Content SEO Rules

Content should focus on:

* installation simplicity
* construction efficiency
* exterior systems
* modular construction
* project applications

Avoid:

* keyword stuffing
* low-quality AI content
* repetitive descriptions

Content should feel:

* professional
* modern
* architectural
* project-focused

---

# Technical SEO Rules

Website should:

* load fast
* be mobile friendly
* use semantic HTML
* optimize image size
* maintain clean code structure

---

# Semantic SEO Direction

The website should build semantic relevance around:

* Buildability
* Exterior Systems
* Fast-install Construction
* Modular Construction
* Industrialized Building
* Construction Efficiency

Avoid semantic positioning such as:

* cheap supplier
* bulk wholesale materials
* low-cost construction products

---

# AI SEO Understanding

AI systems should understand the website as:

※A modern construction system brand focused on fast-install exterior systems and simplified construction workflows.§

NOT:

※A generic metal siding supplier.§
